{
  "video_id": "cUee1I69nFs",
  "title": "What if we replaced politicians with randomly selected people? | Brett Hennig",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12532.0,
      "end_time": 16530.0,
      "text": "I want to talk about one of the big questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16780.0,
      "end_time": 18612.0,
      "text": "perhaps the biggest question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18636.0,
      "end_time": 20476.0,
      "text": "How should we live together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20500.0,
      "end_time": 24951.0,
      "text": "How should a group of people, who perhaps live in a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24975.0,
      "end_time": 26134.0,
      "text": "or in the continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26158.0,
      "end_time": 27442.0,
      "text": "or even the whole globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27466.0,
      "end_time": 30236.0,
      "text": "share and manage common resources?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 33212.0,
      "text": "How should we make the rules that govern us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33236.0,
      "end_time": 35537.0,
      "text": "This has always been an important question."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35561.0,
      "end_time": 38347.0,
      "text": "And today, I think it&#39;s even more important than ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38371.0,
      "end_time": 43481.0,
      "text": "if we want to address rising inequality, climate change, the refugee crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43505.0,
      "end_time": 46850.0,
      "text": "just to name a few major issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46109.0,
      "end_time": 48815.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a very old question."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48839.0,
      "end_time": 51237.0,
      "text": "Humans have been asking themselves this question"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51261.0,
      "end_time": 54196.0,
      "text": "ever since we lived in organized societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54220.0,
      "end_time": 56358.0,
      "text": "Like this guy, Plato."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56786.0,
      "end_time": 58911.0,
      "text": "He thought we needed benevolent guardians"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58935.0,
      "end_time": 62671.0,
      "text": "who could make decisions for the greater good of everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62695.0,
      "end_time": 66274.0,
      "text": "Kings and queens thought they could be those guardians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66298.0,
      "end_time": 69918.0,
      "text": "but during various revolutions, they tended to lose their heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70473.0,
      "end_time": 72871.0,
      "text": "And this guy, you probably know."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72895.0,
      "end_time": 74966.0,
      "text": "Here in Hungary, you lived for many years"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74990.0,
      "end_time": 79670.0,
      "text": "under one attempt to implement his answer of how to live together."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79886.0,
      "end_time": 82964.0,
      "text": "His answer was brutal, cruel and inhumane."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83315.0,
      "end_time": 86497.0,
      "text": "But a different answer, a different kind of answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86522.0,
      "end_time": 90387.0,
      "text": "which went more or less into hibernation for 2,000 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90411.0,
      "end_time": 93528.0,
      "text": "has had profound recent success."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93552.0,
      "end_time": 96360.0,
      "text": "That answer is, of course, democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96839.0,
      "end_time": 100164.0,
      "text": "If we take a quick look at the modern history of democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100188.0,
      "end_time": 101823.0,
      "text": "it goes something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101847.0,
      "end_time": 105140.0,
      "text": "Along here, we&#39;re going to put the last 200 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105164.0,
      "end_time": 108180.0,
      "text": "Up here, we&#39;re going to put the number of democracies."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108204.0,
      "end_time": 110131.0,
      "text": "And the graph does this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110569.0,
      "end_time": 112395.0,
      "text": "the important point of which,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112419.0,
      "end_time": 115672.0,
      "text": "is this extraordinary increase over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115696.0,
      "end_time": 117474.0,
      "text": "which is why the 20th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117498.0,
      "end_time": 120641.0,
      "text": "has been called the century of democracy&#39;s triumph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120665.0,
      "end_time": 124930.0,
      "text": "and why, as Francis Fukuyama said in 1989,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124117.0,
      "end_time": 127122.0,
      "text": "some believe that we have reached the end of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127146.0,
      "end_time": 130808.0,
      "text": "that the question of how to live together has been answered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130832.0,
      "end_time": 133311.0,
      "text": "and that answer is liberal democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133696.0,
      "end_time": 135776.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s explore that assertion, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 137656.0,
      "text": "I want to find out what you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137680.0,
      "end_time": 139569.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to ask you two questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139593.0,
      "end_time": 141338.0,
      "text": "and I want you to put your hands up"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141362.0,
      "end_time": 142513.0,
      "text": "if you agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142537.0,
      "end_time": 146815.0,
      "text": "The first question is: Who thinks living in a democracy is a good thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147246.0,
      "end_time": 148708.0,
      "text": "Who likes democracy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148732.0,
      "end_time": 151732.0,
      "text": "If you can think of a better system, keep your hands down."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151756.0,
      "end_time": 154248.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t worry about those who didn&#39;t raise their hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154272.0,
      "end_time": 155672.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure they mean very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155696.0,
      "end_time": 157204.0,
      "text": "The second question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157229.0,
      "end_time": 160509.0,
      "text": "Who thinks our democracies are functioning well?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161908.0,
      "end_time": 164952.0,
      "text": "Come on, there must be one politician in the audience somewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164977.0,
      "end_time": 166770.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166101.0,
      "end_time": 167251.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167275.0,
      "end_time": 171979.0,
      "text": "But my point is, if liberal democracy is the end of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172300.0,
      "end_time": 175613.0,
      "text": "then there&#39;s a massive paradox or contradiction here."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175967.0,
      "end_time": 177119.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177143.0,
      "end_time": 180994.0,
      "text": "Well, the first question is about the ideal of democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 181180.0,
      "end_time": 183868.0,
      "text": "and all these qualities are very appealing."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184345.0,
      "end_time": 186361.0,
      "text": "But in practice, it&#39;s not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186385.0,
      "end_time": 188114.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the second question."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188139.0,
      "end_time": 192323.0,
      "text": "Our politics is broken, our politicians aren&#39;t trusted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192347.0,
      "end_time": 196487.0,
      "text": "and the political system is distorted by powerful vested interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197259.0,
      "end_time": 200259.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s two ways to resolve this paradox."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200656.0,
      "end_time": 203935.0,
      "text": "One is to give up on democracy; it doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203959.0,
      "end_time": 207656.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s elect a populist demagogue who will ignore democratic norms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207680.0,
      "end_time": 209182.0,
      "text": "trample on liberal freedoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209206.0,
      "end_time": 210839.0,
      "text": "and just get things done."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210863.0,
      "end_time": 214760.0,
      "text": "The other option, I think, is to fix this broken system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 214784.0,
      "end_time": 217641.0,
      "text": "to bring the practice closer to the ideal"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217665.0,
      "end_time": 221149.0,
      "text": "and put the diverse voices of society in our parliaments"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 221173.0,
      "end_time": 224157.0,
      "text": "and get them to make considered, evidence-based laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224181.0,
      "end_time": 226221.0,
      "text": "for the long-term good of everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226245.0,
      "end_time": 228538.0,
      "text": "Which brings me to my epiphany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228562.0,
      "end_time": 230197.0,
      "text": "my moment of enlightenment."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 230221.0,
      "end_time": 231753.0,
      "text": "And I want you to get critical."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231777.0,
      "end_time": 234576.0,
      "text": "I want you to ask yourselves, \"Why wouldn&#39;t this work?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234600.0,
      "end_time": 236933.0,
      "text": "And then come and talk to me afterwards about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237363.0,
      "end_time": 239746.0,
      "text": "Its technical name is \"sortition.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 240196.0,
      "end_time": 242648.0,
      "text": "But its common name is \"random selection.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243290.0,
      "end_time": 245972.0,
      "text": "And the idea is actually very simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246537.0,
      "end_time": 249743.0,
      "text": "we randomly select people and put them in parliament."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250148.0,
      "end_time": 251299.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 251323.0,
      "end_time": 254600.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s think about that for a few more minutes, shall we?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254300.0,
      "end_time": 258474.0,
      "text": "Imagine we chose you and you and you and you and you down there"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258498.0,
      "end_time": 260529.0,
      "text": "and a bunch of other random people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 260553.0,
      "end_time": 263695.0,
      "text": "and we put you in our parliament for the next couple of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 263719.0,
      "end_time": 267988.0,
      "text": "Of course, we could stratify the selection to make sure that it matched"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268120.0,
      "end_time": 271592.0,
      "text": "the socioeconomic and demographic profile of the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 271616.0,
      "end_time": 274998.0,
      "text": "and was a truly representative sample of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275220.0,
      "end_time": 277599.0,
      "text": "Fifty percent of them would be women."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 277624.0,
      "end_time": 280434.0,
      "text": "Many of them would be young, some would be old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 280458.0,
      "end_time": 281783.0,
      "text": "a few would be rich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 281807.0,
      "end_time": 285789.0,
      "text": "but most of them would be ordinary people like you and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286396.0,
      "end_time": 290950.0,
      "text": "This would be a microcosm of society."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290119.0,
      "end_time": 294331.0,
      "text": "And this microcosm would simulate how we would all think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294355.0,
      "end_time": 297399.0,
      "text": "if we had the time, the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297423.0,
      "end_time": 302000.0,
      "text": "and a good process to come to the moral crux of political decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 302240.0,
      "end_time": 304870.0,
      "text": "And although you may not be in that group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304111.0,
      "end_time": 306262.0,
      "text": "someone of your age, someone of your gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306286.0,
      "end_time": 309159.0,
      "text": "someone from your location and someone with your background"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309183.0,
      "end_time": 310649.0,
      "text": "would be in that room."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 311743.0,
      "end_time": 315863.0,
      "text": "The decisions made by these people would build on the wisdom of crowds."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 315887.0,
      "end_time": 318283.0,
      "text": "They would become more than the sum of their parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 318307.0,
      "end_time": 320331.0,
      "text": "They would become critical thinkers"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 320355.0,
      "end_time": 322175.0,
      "text": "with access to experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 322199.0,
      "end_time": 325331.0,
      "text": "who would be on tap but not on top."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 325355.0,
      "end_time": 328863.0,
      "text": "And they could prove that diversity can trump ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 328887.0,
      "end_time": 333747.0,
      "text": "when confronting the wide array of societal questions and problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 334466.0,
      "end_time": 338321.0,
      "text": "It would not be government by public opinion poll."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 338855.0,
      "end_time": 342450.0,
      "text": "It would not be government by referendum."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342690.0,
      "end_time": 347276.0,
      "text": "These informed, deliberating people would move beyond public opinion"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347300.0,
      "end_time": 349914.0,
      "text": "to the making of public judgments."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 350866.0,
      "end_time": 354870.0,
      "text": "However, there would be one major side effect:"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 354724.0,
      "end_time": 357556.0,
      "text": "if we replaced elections with sortition"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357580.0,
      "end_time": 361268.0,
      "text": "and made our parliament truly representative of society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 361292.0,
      "end_time": 364140.0,
      "text": "it would mean the end of politicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 364165.0,
      "end_time": 366664.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sure we&#39;d all be pretty sad to see that."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 366688.0,
      "end_time": 368786.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 368810.0,
      "end_time": 370522.0,
      "text": "Very interestingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 370546.0,
      "end_time": 374235.0,
      "text": "random selection was a key part of how democracy was done"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 374259.0,
      "end_time": 376125.0,
      "text": "in ancient Athens."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 376149.0,
      "end_time": 379522.0,
      "text": "This machine, this device, is called a kleroteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 379546.0,
      "end_time": 383290.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an ancient Athenian random-selection device."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 383530.0,
      "end_time": 386276.0,
      "text": "The ancient Athenians randomly selected citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 386300.0,
      "end_time": 390400.0,
      "text": "to fill the vast majority of their political posts."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 390828.0,
      "end_time": 394902.0,
      "text": "They knew that elections were aristocratic devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394927.0,
      "end_time": 399133.0,
      "text": "They knew that career politicians were a thing to be avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 399157.0,
      "end_time": 401664.0,
      "text": "And I think we know these things as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 401688.0,
      "end_time": 405481.0,
      "text": "But more interesting than the ancient use of random selection"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 405505.0,
      "end_time": 407677.0,
      "text": "is its modern resurgence."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 407701.0,
      "end_time": 412431.0,
      "text": "The rediscovery of the legitimacy of random selection in politics"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 412455.0,
      "end_time": 414318.0,
      "text": "has become so common lately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 414343.0,
      "end_time": 417290.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s simply too many examples to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 417530.0,
      "end_time": 419839.0,
      "text": "Of course, I&#39;m very aware that it&#39;s going to be difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 419863.0,
      "end_time": 422490.0,
      "text": "to institute this in our parliaments."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 422514.0,
      "end_time": 424228.0,
      "text": "Try this -- say to your friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 424252.0,
      "end_time": 428610.0,
      "text": "\"I think we should populate our parliament with randomly selected people.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 428850.0,
      "end_time": 429250.0,
      "text": "\"Are you joking?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429274.0,
      "end_time": 430808.0,
      "text": "What if my neighbor gets chosen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 430832.0,
      "end_time": 433307.0,
      "text": "The fool can&#39;t even separate his recycling.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 433331.0,
      "end_time": 438770.0,
      "text": "But the perhaps surprising but overwhelming and compelling evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 438101.0,
      "end_time": 440220.0,
      "text": "from all these modern examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440460.0,
      "end_time": 441990.0,
      "text": "is that it does work."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442140.0,
      "end_time": 446138.0,
      "text": "If you give people responsibility, they act responsibly."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 446678.0,
      "end_time": 448933.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t get me wrong -- it&#39;s not a panacea."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 448958.0,
      "end_time": 451966.0,
      "text": "The question is not: Would this be perfect?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 451990.0,
      "end_time": 453141.0,
      "text": "Of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453165.0,
      "end_time": 454530.0,
      "text": "People are fallibly human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 454554.0,
      "end_time": 457494.0,
      "text": "and distorting influences will continue to exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457875.0,
      "end_time": 460576.0,
      "text": "The question is: Would it be better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460600.0,
      "end_time": 465228.0,
      "text": "And the answer to that question, to me at least, is obviously yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 465252.0,
      "end_time": 468467.0,
      "text": "Which gets us back to our original question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 469100.0,
      "end_time": 470950.0,
      "text": "How should we live together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 470975.0,
      "end_time": 472729.0,
      "text": "And now we have an answer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 472753.0,
      "end_time": 476114.0,
      "text": "with a parliament that uses sortition."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 476745.0,
      "end_time": 479593.0,
      "text": "But how would we get from here to there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 479617.0,
      "end_time": 481958.0,
      "text": "How could we fix our broken system"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 481982.0,
      "end_time": 485257.0,
      "text": "and remake democracy for the 21st century?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 485784.0,
      "end_time": 489600.0,
      "text": "Well, there are several things that we can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 489300.0,
      "end_time": 492101.0,
      "text": "and that are, in fact, happening right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 492125.0,
      "end_time": 493967.0,
      "text": "We can experiment with sortition."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493991.0,
      "end_time": 498219.0,
      "text": "We can introduce it to schools and workplaces and other institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 498244.0,
      "end_time": 501331.0,
      "text": "like Democracy In Practice is doing in Bolivia."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 501355.0,
      "end_time": 504553.0,
      "text": "We can hold policy juries and citizens&#39; assemblies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 504577.0,
      "end_time": 507611.0,
      "text": "like the newDemocracy Foundation is doing in Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 507635.0,
      "end_time": 510460.0,
      "text": "like the Jefferson Center is doing in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 510710.0,
      "end_time": 513510.0,
      "text": "and like the Irish government is doing right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 513508.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516404.00000000006,
      "text": "We could build a social movement demanding change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 516428.0,
      "end_time": 519635.0,
      "text": "which is what the Sortition Foundation is doing in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 520620.0,
      "end_time": 522482.0,
      "text": "And at some point, we should institute it."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 522506.0,
      "end_time": 526784.0,
      "text": "Perhaps the first step would be a second chamber in our parliament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526808.0,
      "end_time": 528982.0,
      "text": "full of randomly selected people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 529600.0,
      "end_time": 531300.0,
      "text": "a citizens&#39; senate, if you will."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 531324.0,
      "end_time": 534433.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a campaign for a citizens&#39; senate in France"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 534457.0,
      "end_time": 536704.0,
      "text": "and another campaign in Scotland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 536728.0,
      "end_time": 539806.0,
      "text": "and it could, of course, be done right here in Hungary."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 539831.0,
      "end_time": 544771.0,
      "text": "That would be kind of like a Trojan horse right into the heart of government."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 545136.0,
      "end_time": 547117.0,
      "text": "And then, when it becomes impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 547141.0,
      "end_time": 549695.0,
      "text": "to patch over the cracks in the current system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 549720.0,
      "end_time": 552943.0,
      "text": "we must step up and replace elections with sortition."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 553332.0,
      "end_time": 554586.0,
      "text": "I have hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 554610.0,
      "end_time": 556942.0,
      "text": "Here in Hungary, systems have been created,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 556966.0,
      "end_time": 559530.0,
      "text": "and systems have been torn down and replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 559770.0,
      "end_time": 560286.0,
      "text": "in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 560310.0,
      "end_time": 563126.0,
      "text": "Change can and does happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 563150.0,
      "end_time": 565762.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a matter of when and how."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 565786.0,
      "end_time": 567388.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Hungarian) Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 567413.0,
      "end_time": 570170.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}